narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A senior essay. Exactly what it sounds like. You have to do it, so do it in the fall and get it over with. It was alternately stupid and incredibly fulfilling. Make it constantly fulfilling and you'll be a happy person.

Keep on top of your research throughout the semester- I know it's hard to stay that disciplined, but it will make the last few weeks of the semester and your Thanksgiving break SO much more enjoyable. And you need to get your rough draft in before Thanksgiving- so keep in mind how quickly the months of September and October fly by.
it is a requirement of the major.
I mean, you have to do it if you're a HSAR major. Turn in a first draft.
Well, to graduate with an Art History degree you have to write your thesis. I recommend doing a lot of work early on and not delaying to the last minute. It is brutal, but a lot of fun.
